{"type": "article", "id": 10346, "title": "Infinity 灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-03T08:32:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235523x6oDJFgIcpMyah1L.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">设计师 Leonardo Criolani 推出的这款灯名为 “Infinity”，内含着设计师对于“无穷”的探索和理解，两个外涂白漆的金属LED灯彼此缠绕，从不同的角度看过去，灯具会呈现不同的角度，从而带来不同的体验，同时圆形的设计也包含“无穷无尽”的含义。这是<a href=\"http://www.leonardocriolani.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看详细信息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235521UqO2W4swMTHd6phD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235521sQiVTlwygfembSBI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355213B1oSHqaiTdx7JM4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235522HG3yCSLD81ZuieUm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235522BuaXYJVgHQryeUlz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.91687042\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235522Y7yXWkIbVTng5DGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65403423\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}